snippet.textDisplay: Every once in a very blue moon do we have a chance to study such a performer. She is a haunting child. Her melodies make your soul cry. This performance is no exception. Her brother is an integral part of her as a performer. He rounds every performance. They have written another dark, brooding, masterpiece with Time To Die. Billie breaths her edge into whatever she sings. Sing on nightingale. We will brave the dark to hear your wounded heart.
